library(readxl)
library(ggplot2)
df <- read_excel("C:/Users/User/Downloads/Ukraine_Black_Sea_2020_2022_Jun03.xlsx")
#View(Ukraine_Black_Sea_2020_2022_Jun03)
LAT <- df$"LATITUDE"
LAG <- df$"LONGITUDE"

ggplot(df, aes(x = LAG, y = LAT)) + 
  geom_point(size = 0.5,colour = "purple") + 
  coord_equal() + 
  xlab('Longitude') + 
  ylab('Latitude')
